# 檢查現有監控器的腳本

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:9091
@apiKey = uk1_dRoog_hjdvwvtQTCwXeaXj2jbrjA0OVOsLIkSwJn

### 1. 查看所有監控器
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/monitors
Authorization: {{apiKey}}

### 2. 查看 API 狀態
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/status

### 3. 創建一些測試監控器（如果需要更多監控器的話）

### 創建監控器 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/monitors
Authorization: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試監控器_1",
  "type": "http",
  "url": "https://httpbin.org/status/200",
  "interval": 60,
  "active": true,
  "method": "GET"
}

### 創建監控器 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/monitors
Authorization: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試監控器_2",
  "type": "ping",
  "hostname": "8.8.8.8",
  "interval": 60,
  "active": true
}

### 創建監控器 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/monitors
Authorization: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試監控器_3",
  "type": "dns",
  "hostname": "google.com",
  "interval": 60,
  "active": true
}
